## 1. Architecture Overview

```
Teacher (Google Form / Sheet)
        │
        ▼
  GAS Trigger fires on form submission
        │
        ▼
   fetchLivePrice(asin)           ← Product Search API[1]
        │
        ▼
   priceTolerance(submitted, live)[2]
        │
        ├── BOUNCE_BACK → email teacher → halt
        │
        ├── WITHIN_TOLERANCE → adjustBudget() → continue
        │
        └── AUTO_APPROVE (live ≤ submitted) → continue
        │
        ▼
   placeOrder(asin, qty, livePrice) ← Ordering API[3]
        │
        ├── rejectedItems → parse BrokenUnitPriceExpectation → email office
        │
        └── acceptedItems → log orderId, unitPrice, delivery range
        │
        ▼
   logToSheet(orderResult)
        │
        ▼
